WEIGHTING FORMULA..
Solve for w_1, w_2: [scale_1 ^ w_1 / pages_1 ^ w_2] == [scale_2 ^ w_1 / pages_2 ^ w_2]
Or minimize (-1 + [scale_1 ^ w_1 / pages_1 ^ w_2] * [scale_2 ^ w_1 / pages_2 ^ w_2] * [scale_3 ^ w_1 / pages_3 ^ w_2] ... * [scale_n ^ w_1 / pages_n ^ w_2]
)^2
Ex: If you want to split the page when scaling is smaller than 0.7
Condition 1: scale_1 = 0.7 pages_1 = 1 Condition 2: scale_2 = 1.0 pages_2 = 2
Solve: [(.7 ^ w_1) / (1^w_2)] = [(1 ^ w_1) / (2^w_2)]
w2 => 0.514573 w1 w1 = 1.94336 w2 = 1
